  "display_name": "Economic Growth and Development",
  "description": "This cluster of papers explores the intersection of information and communication technology (ICT), financial access, inequality, and knowledge economy in the context of African countries. It investigates the role of mobile phones, governance, and education in promoting inclusive development and gender inclusion, while also examining the impact of ICT on institutional quality and economic growth.",
